<node CREATED="1311424626171" ID="Freemind_Link_594970459" MODIFIED="1311424780406" POSITION="right" TEXT="&#x4e3b;&#x6d41;&#x6d4f;&#x89c8;&#x5668;&#x652f;&#x6301;&#x7684;js&#x7248;&#x672c;&#xa;1&#x3001;IE 6-7 support JScript 5 (which is equivalent to ECMAScript 3, JavaScript 1.5)&#xa;2&#x3001;IE 8 supports JScript 6 (which is equivalent to ECMAScript 3, JavaScript 1.5 &#x2013; more bug fixes over JScript 5)&#xa;3&#x3001;Firefox 1.0 supports JavaScript 1.5 (ECMAScript 3 equivalent)&#xa;4&#x3001;Firefox 1.5 supports JavaScript 1.6 (1.5 + Array Extras + E4X + misc.)&#xa;5&#x3001;Firefox 2.0 supports JavaScript 1.7 (1.6 + Generator + Iterators + let + misc.)&#xa;6&#x3001;Firefox 3.0 supports JavaScript 1.8 (1.7 + Generator Expressions + Expression Closures + misc.)&#xa;7&#x3001;The next version of Firefox will support JavaScript 1.9 (1.8 + To be determined)&#xa;8&#x3001;Opera supports a language that is equivalent to ECMAScript 3 + Getters and Setters + misc.&#xa;9&#x3001;Safari supports a language that is equivalent to ECMAScript 3 + Getters and Setters + misc."/>
